I Know You Know]

42:22.470 --> 42:24.199
* I KNOW YOU KNOW

42:24.240 --> 42:26.162
* THAT I'M NOT
TELLING THE TRUTH *

42:26.210 --> 42:27.700
* I KNOW YOU KNOW

42:27.740 --> 42:29.230
* THEY JUST
DON'T HAVE ANY PROOF *

42:29.280 --> 42:30.838
* EMBRACE THE DECEPTION

42:30.880 --> 42:32.438
* LEARN HOW TO BEND

42:32.480 --> 42:33.902
* YOUR WORST INHIBITIONS

42:33.950 --> 42:36.669
* TEND TO
